    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2154570/extras/e648b875e3f03aebe40baa32c01766c1.apng?t=1712372420\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2154570/extras/e648b875e3f03aebe40baa32c01766c1.poster.avif?t=1712372420\" class=\"bb_img\" width=256 height=32 /></picture></span><br>Alice, the reaper girl, found herself lost in the Underworld! She must escape this forgotten land before the corruption takes over everything, but she's not alone!<br>With the help of a Soulvolver, a weapon capable of shooting souls, and her new friends, Alice will face the dangers and become, once and for all, a Soulslinger.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2154570/extras/2ae9b9338b4a23cece4055055f69ec55.apng?t=1712372420\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2154570/extras/2ae9b9338b4a23cece4055055f69ec55.poster.avif?t=1712372420\" class=\"bb_img\" width=256 height=32 /></picture></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Reaping an enemy soul will recover your Soulvolver ammo!<br></li><li>Destroying obstacles and defeating enemies helps the level progression, the more you destroy, the faster you'll progress!<br></li><li>Blessings and curses are permanent power ups, each one with it's own special effect!<br></li><li>Pies are consumable temporary power ups, each one with it's own purpose; use them wisely!</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2154570/extras/2082fca0d0a7f4bed5600e4749c3ad70.apng?t=1712372420\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2154570/extras/2082fca0d0a7f4bed5600e4749c3ad70.poster.avif?t=1712372420\" class=\"bb_img\" width=256 height=32 /></picture></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Three levels of difficulty;<br></li><li>Five stages, each one with its own boss;<br></li><li>Three special soulblasters to use;<br></li><li>Nineteen different blessings to obtain;<br></li><li>Five flavors of pies;<br></li><li>Five playable characters skins;<br></li><li>20+ hats to collect;<br></li><li>Endless mode.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2154570/extras/0043a08f78d15a170e40d0fdad581057.apng?t=1712372420\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2154570/extras/0043a08f78d15a170e40d0fdad581057.poster.avif?t=1712372420\" class=\"bb_img\" width=256 height=32 /></picture></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>WASD or Arrow Keys - Move<br></li><li>Left Mouse Button - Attack<br></li><li>Hold left mouse button for autoswing<br></li><li>Right Mouse Button - Switch weapon<br></li><li>Shift or Space - Use pie<br></li><li>P or Esc - Pause<br></li><li>Enter - Confirm<br></li><li>F4 - Toggle fullscreen</li></ul><br><strong>Controller:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Left Stick or Direction Pad - Move<br></li><li>A, X, Shoulders or Triggers - Attack<br></li><li>Right Stick - Move cursor, aim and switch weapon<br></li><li>B or Y - Use pie<br></li><li>Start - Pause<br></li><li>A - Confirm<br></li><li>Back - Open Steam Friends</li></ul>",
